# G relation

Wire a GORM association between two resources.

1. Ask the user for `<Resource> belongs_to|has_many|has_one
   <OtherResource>`.
2. Run `gofasta g relation <args> --dry-run --json` to preview.
3. Show the user the model edits and the foreign-key migration.
4. Re-run without `--dry-run` to apply if approved.
